# Templates Rules

## Required Structure
- All templates must have at least one section to work properly in the theme editor
- The minimum valid template structure is:
  ```json
  {
    "sections": {
      "section_name": {
        "type": "section_type"
      }
    },
    "order": [
      "section_name"
    ]
  }
  ```

## Best Practices
- Use meaningful section names that reflect their purpose
- Keep the order array in sync with the sections object
- Consider using a common section like custom_code as a placeholder when no specific section is needed
- Always include both the sections object and order array in JSON templates

